<i>noun</i>: 행인 [행인], 보행자 [보ː행자] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>행인 [행인]</dt><br>
<dd>passerby; pedestrian</dd><br>
<dd>길을 가는 사람.</dd><br>
<dd>A person who happens to walk by a certain place.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>보행자 [보ː행자]</dt><br>
<dd>pedestrian; walker</dd><br>
<dd>길거리를 걸어 다니는 사람.</dd><br>
<dd>A person who walks in a street.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>